    </sentence>
    <sentence id="DDI-MedLine.d103.s5" text="Physiological oral magnesium supplementation (5 mg/kg/day) is easy and can be carried out in the diet or with magnesium salts, with practically only one contra-indication: overt renal failure. ">
        <entity id="DDI-MedLine.d103.s5.e0" charOffset="19-27"
